overview:
Since 2008, Gigastar Lighting Co., Ltd has been a progressive developer and innovator of LED Light Bulbs, LED Lighting Products, and LED Tubes. We use Epistar LED Chip (Taiwan), Sanan LED Chip (China) or Cree LED Chip (USA)

We have since expanded our manufacturing operations from Hong Kong to Shenzhen (China Mainland). Today, our Shenzhen factory, with one R&D office and international customer service network has 90 employees to serve our growing client base worldwide.

Our staff of engineers, technicians and customer service specialists are trained, motivated and dedicated to keeping your world constant and ensuring your business continuity through our High Quality product lines of LED Lighting Products.
